1
00:00:01,560 --> 00:00:06,140
Same bed but it feels just
a little bit bigger now

2
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:13,696
Our song on the radio but
it don't sound the same

3
00:00:15,776 --> 00:00:18,229
When our friends talk about you

4
00:00:18,229 --> 00:00:21,859
All it does is just tear me down

5
00:00:23,193 --> 00:00:26,060
'Cause my heart breaks a little

6
00:00:26,060 --> 00:00:28,510
When I hear your name

7
00:00:28,510 --> 00:00:37,381
It all just sounds like ooh-ooh, ooh-ooh

8
00:00:37,459 --> 00:00:43,220
Mmm, too young, too dumb to realize

9
00:00:43,220 --> 00:00:47,135
That I should've bought you flowers

10
00:00:47,810 --> 00:00:50,420
And held your hand

11
00:00:50,420 --> 00:00:53,888
Should've gave you all my hours

12
00:00:54,496 --> 00:00:57,279
When I had the chance

13
00:00:57,760 --> 00:01:00,261
Take you to every party

14
00:01:00,261 --> 00:01:05,088
'Cause all you wanted to do was dance

15
00:01:05,088 --> 00:01:08,267
Now my baby's dancing

16
00:01:08,659 --> 00:01:13,290
But she's dancing with another man

